Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minta tolong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tergantung permintaannya, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kamu mengumpulkan\Nbijih mithril dari gunung di timur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asalkan ada peta untuk ke gunung itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah sepakat, material bawaanmu\Nkuhargai 360 ribu rave, bagaimana?
