Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana suka muncul monster,\Nkuserahkan padamu, Pengumpul Material.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, muncul monster juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya bisa santai juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pengin mandi atau berendam sekalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membawakan air panas\Nsebagai pelayan penginapan.
