Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk membasuh badan atau kaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Badan Tuan Pengembara penuh debu, kan?
