Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu siapa kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi daya sihirmu\Nsepertinya setara denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:17:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, maaf, jangan-jangan kamu\Nadalah Ancient Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Voldius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vo-Volcan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, bolehkah kupanggil Vol saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takeru, aku ingin meminjam kekuatanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kekuatanmu yang murni,\Nmungkin anakku bisa bangkit kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibangkitkan kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena elemen magis yang mengendap,\Ntelurnya jadi tidak mau menetas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja ada imbalannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bijih magis mithril?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, mana telur yang katamu\Ntidak mau menetas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ge-Gede banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vol, harus aku apakan telur ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alirkan daya sihirmu,\Nseperti saat membuat cahaya itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm, karena ini telur,\Ncukup kuhangatkan saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vol, bahagia sekali ketawamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal... aku masih belum lama...\Ndatang ke dunia lain ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku ingin... menjelajahi...\Nlebih banyak dunia lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ceroboh juga, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sang Dewa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, bukan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya, kalau muncul naga,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang akan pingsan\Natau kabur terbirit-birit, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar, belum apa-apa,\Nsudah mengubah logika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya tidak suka\Nsudah bekerja ratusan ribu tahun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dalam sekejap,\Nkamu sudah membuat ombak menyebar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kukurangi berkah konyol\Nyang sudah anak itu berikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, biar kuingatkan, kamu sendiri\Nyang memintanya, partner yang manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, lagi-lagi pandanganku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu perlu sedikit kesusahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha? Apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Byui!\N- Iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}E-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Vol?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya aku sudah kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi-lagi mengeluarkan suara konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karaktermu bukan begitu, kan, Vol?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Byui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak Vol sudah menetas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Byui, byui!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan jilati aku!\NJangan gigit juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, bau!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namailah dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, memberinya nama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa bukan kamu saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia punya nama asli, tapi aku ingin\Nkamu memberinya nama panggilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Black", tapi dijadikan Bee saja,\Nbagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mudah disebut dan rasanya cocok buatmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kamu senang, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, bau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Black Nobee Voldius,\Nkamu dapat nama yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, Bee dari "Black".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Black Nobee, pergi dan jelajahilah\Ndunia yang luas ini sepuas hatimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:14.04,tanda,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ANAKAN ANCIENT DRAGON - BLACK NOBEE VOLDIUS\NTELAH MENJADI TEMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa mau menitipkan anak tersayangmu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke orang asing sepertiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa tenang menitipkannya pada dirimu\Nyang punya kekuatan lebih besar dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, sakit, bau pula.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuserahkan padamu, Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau tidak, ikut denganku melakukan\Nperjalanan mengumpulkan material?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, sepakat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sebelum itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Clean!
